{"tid":966743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬英九:一中是中華民國 兩岸目前難統一","createTime":"2019-01-03T04:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T05:50:29.000Z","uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"888c52283f88510db327857d16b901bd31fb0954","tid":966743,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平昨日提出用「一國兩制」的構想實現台海統一，強調堅持「九二共識」，又不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n台灣前總統馬英九認為「九二共識」的精神，就是「一個中國，各自表述」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「一中」是中華民國</span></strong>，又指雖然不排除統一，但目前兩岸還不具備統一條件，未來也要循和平方式和民主程序，由全體台灣人民共同決定。<br />\n<br />\n馬英九認為，「一國兩制」在台灣一直沒有市場，而對於習近平提到中國人不打中國人，就是對台獨非常明確的訊息。"},{"pid":"8c425f5454ac8dd8a529aba0d0c52d36552d3631","tid":966743,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"連馬英九都唔同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa8712bec874e86286b382ddb3349957e4b03d4","tid":966743,"uid":46943,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8c425f5454ac8dd8a529aba0d0c52d36552d3631","tid":966743,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"連馬英九都唔同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"佢同意不過唔俾共"},{"pid":"7e42533bd81d4f3c634861ad593dd911f098336d","tid":966743,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢唔是奶工嫁咩"},{"pid":"fa09227d5fecc9b57337b9321e01d8263670b133","tid":966743,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e42533bd81d4f3c634861ad593dd911f098336d","tid":966743,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 